				<tr>
				
					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p154289">SNES register sizing schemes (65816 M and X)</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=154289&amp;sid=c74ae457b5988db6f2d20406dd9598fb#p154289"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Sat Aug 29, 2015 6:28 am&nbsp;</div></td>
